oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Message from R. E. Winsett to Roy Acuff - Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 1 of a message recorded by gospel music composer R. E. Winsett giving Roy Acuff permission to record his songs. R. E. Winsett also discusses his home-recording equipment, and transcribes excerpts of two of Roy Acuff's recordings.
